        "직접 비트를 작곡하고 사운드를 설계하고 믹싱/마스터링까지 하는 비트 제작 미니 DAW.",
        "It can support sampling later as an optional extension, but the identity, first-run workflow, MVP proof, and core architecture are direct beat production.",
        "The center is writing and shaping the beat directly.",
